{"title":"2020-12-20 宝達山周回","virttualPath":null,"html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-2020-12-20-宝達山周回\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2020-12-20-%E5%AE%9D%E9%81%94%E5%B1%B1%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9E\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>2020-12-20 宝達山周回</h1>\n<p>とりあえず、今年の初雪を踏みたかったのでぐるっと周回してきた。</p>\n<p>宝達山</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-114204-P_20201220_114204.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-114204-P_20201220_114204.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>トレースは一人分</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-115400-P_20201220_115400.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-115400-P_20201220_115400.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>真っ白</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-115406-P_20201220_115406_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-115406-P_20201220_115406_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>真っ白！</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-120723-P_20201220_120723_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-120723-P_20201220_120723_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>昨日、今日で山頂域を歩いてるのは私だけ。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-120731-P_20201220_120731.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-120731-P_20201220_120731.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>樹氷が美しい</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-121230-P_20201220_121230.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-121230-P_20201220_121230.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2020/2020-12-20/20201220-121230-P_20201220_121230.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-122001-P_20201220_122001.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-122001-P_20201220_122001.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"一等三角点\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>邪魔だった雨量測定は吊り上げ？て上に行ったらしい。前の死ぬほど邪魔だった子は仮置きだったわけね…</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-122010-P_20201220_122009.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-122010-P_20201220_122009.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-122723-P_20201220_122723.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-122723-P_20201220_122723.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>今年は凍った。去年はほんとに雪少なかった。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-125530-P_20201220_125530.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-125530-P_20201220_125530.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>誰もいない</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-125538-P_20201220_125538.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-125538-P_20201220_125538.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>この辺りで猟師が車でウロウロしてった。何してるのかと思ったけど、猪が罠にかかってるか見に行ったのかな？</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-133348-P_20201220_133348_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-133348-P_20201220_133348_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>麓はこんな感じ</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2020-12-20/20201220-140517-P_20201220_140517.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-12-20/20201220-140517-P_20201220_140517.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>結局、会ったのはお一人だけ。麓に新しく車があったから、追加でもう一人、二人登ってたのだろう。静かに登れるよいシーズン到来。</p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"随筆","updated":"2020-12-21T22:20:18","published":"2020-12-21T02:54:07"}